code: import axios from'axios';const API_BASE_URL='http://localhost:9999';const getAllMembers=()=>{return axios.get("".concat(API_BASE_URL));};const searchMembers=params=>{return axios.get("".concat(API_BASE_URL,"/admin/search"),{params});};const updateMember=member=>{return axios.put("".concat(API_BASE_URL,"/admin/update"),member);};const deleteMember=memberId=>{return axios.delete("".concat(API_BASE_URL,"/admin/").concat(memberId));};const MemberService={getAllMembers,searchMembers,updateMember,deleteMember};export default MemberService;
